commit_list.message:
Re-set default values after a reload.

Otherwise an instance will no longer respond to the expected methods after a reload.

Ensure we save a record with the primary key on update_all.

The record may have expired under us, if we don't set the primary key the model stored in Redis will be broken.

Avoid shadowing the `key` method.
Add #delete.
Split automatic ID generation into a module.
Version bump.
Refactor and add some Sequel-esqe features.
Fix the gemspec so bundler will use it.

Remove hardcoded port variable

The PORT variable is already set by the Dockerfile, duplicating it here will cause confusion.

Avoid pauses due to localhost resolution/IPv6

When using localhost for the upstream address nginx will print warnings that it was unable to connect to [:::1]:5000 and there are noticeable delays while answering requests. Using 127.0.0.1 stops the warnings and the delays.

Fix nginx.pid path

/var/run/nginx isn't created by the ubuntu nginx package which means nginx will fail to start in containers built from this image. Ubuntu expects to use /run/nginx.pid (which is included in the default nginx.conf).
